{"tid":2324851,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黎智英將於本月23日就兩案向高等法院申請保釋","createTime":"2020-12-14T08:38:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T13:19:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fb6a0fcaa4aca2cd5bf77a2908168b987f9485a9","tid":2324851,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T08:38:49.000Z","msg":"壹傳媒創辦人黎智英被指違反工業邨用地租賃條款，本月3日被控欺詐，還柙候訊，原本已排期本周二即明天向高等法院申請保釋。惟國安處於保釋聆訊4天前，再起訴黎勾結外國或境外勢力危害國家安全罪，提堂後不准保釋。正因兩案而遭還柙的黎，據了解已申請押後原定明天處理的欺詐案保釋申請。根據司法機構網頁顯示，申請已押後至本月23日，相信屆時將合併處理欺詐及國安法兩案的保釋。<br />\n<br />\n現年73歲的黎智英被控一項勾結外國或境外勢力危害國家安全罪，指他今年7月1日至12月1日期間，在香港請求外國或境外機構、組織、人員實施對香港特別行政區或中華人民共和國進行制裁、封鎖或採取其他敵對行動，違反港版國安法第29(4)條。案件上周六在西九龍裁判法院提堂，國安法指定法官之一、總裁判官蘇惠德拒絕讓他保釋候訊，案件押後至4月16日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201214/3MFSCI6KAVE6TMVBLU26NLGDDY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201214%2F3MFSCI6KAVE6TMVBLU26NLGDDY%2F&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725G0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=ca7dc0e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201214%2F3MFSCI6KAVE6TMVBLU26NLGDDY%2F&h=a4298227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201214/3MFSCI6KAVE6TMVBLU26NLGDDY/</a>"},{"pid":"6b175ff7a2d56e14d61142d36baaaa8d8362f458","tid":2324851,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T08:39:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bc525dd6dcb1040fc70a059f2043d4bfdb1bc73","tid":2324851,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T08:56:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f41dd06281f07befc88dd8a4632f874215d61c3b","tid":2324851,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12